{"body": "This is quite a special edge case because of the way BigDecimals are JSON-encoded as strings: https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/activesupport/lib/active_support/json/encoding.rb#L189\r\n\r\nA more generic implementation would test whether the value is already surrounded by double quotes before adding the double quotes in `attrs << %{data-#{k.to_s.dasherize}=\"#{v}\"}` imo, but your version works so I can't argue :)\r\n\r\n+1", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1552436", "created_at": "2011-07-12T07:16:37Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2036#issuecomment-1552436", "updated_at": "2011-07-12T07:16:37Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2036, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/chuyeow", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/00fd4ce27c06ba63e7ddca4c3d67e5ea?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F979d472a84804b9f647bc185a877a8b5.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/received_events", "gravatar_id": "00fd4ce27c06ba63e7ddca4c3d67e5ea", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "chuyeow", "type": "User", "id": 213, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chuyeow/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52384934bd3543c1510111e7"}, "id": 1552436, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2036"}
